  "texts": [
    "This includes questions such as which part of the design process would benefit and be elevated using GenAI.",
    "Therefore we conducted a preliminary study to support the design and development process of DesignPrompt.",
    "We conducted a preliminary study to better understand how visual thinkers could incorporate GenAI into their moodboard process.",
    "We focused on users' interaction and workflow with existing moodboard tools, and how they phrase GenAI text prompts for visual ideation and respond to the generated results.Participants We recruited eight participants (5 women, 3 men; age [23][24][25][26][27][28][29][30].",
    "Four had design backgrounds (P1, P2, P6, P8) and four had engineering backgrounds."
  ]
}